<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَنَّهُ الْحَقُّ}</span> ... أَنَّ القُرْآنَ حَقٌّ لَا رَيْبَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَوَلَمْ يَكْفِ بِرَبِّكَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَلَا يَكْفِيهِمْ دَلَالَةً عَلَى أَنَّ القُرْآنَ حَقٌّ:</span> شَهَادَةُ اللهِ لَهُ بِذَلِكَ؟!<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِرْيَةٍ}</span> ... شَكٍّ عَظِيمٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>